{"type": "article", "id": 25455, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-14T10:53:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26243, "name": "欧冠"}, {"id": 9003, "name": "米兰设计周"}, {"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 3462, "name": "奥巴马"}, {"id": 2105, "name": "科比"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103028nbPDJXT7oVQz6ruC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、白宫科学展</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103016chVXdaWFspkDeYOi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">SAUL LOEB/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在白宫科学展上，美国总统奥巴马用 3D 打印的泡泡棒“吹泡泡”。据悉，这是由来自马里兰州的 9 岁孩子 Jacob Leggette（左）所制作的。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、“一个好总统”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103017tR4FeD1mLVI2Jqpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">美国民主党候选人伯纳德·桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）在纽约玛丽斯特学院（Marist College）的竞选集会上发言，一个小男孩举着一块手写着“伯尼会是一个好总统”的指示牌。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、印尼跳伞训练</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210301702Ob9AtrX7FBajVu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一名印度尼西亚快速反应突击部队（Rapid Reaction Strike Force）的士兵在训练中从飞机上一跃而下。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、告别科比</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103018DFhxH34bY9cXr6jv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在洛杉矶的湖人队周边店，粉丝在一张科比的图片前拍照留念。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、欧冠 1/4 决赛</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030186Dy58vdcXiEwjnIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">CESAR MANSO/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">15/16 欧冠 1/4 决赛次回合，马德里竞技 2-0 巴塞罗那。<br></p>\n<h2>米兰设计周</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103019EcwPhM1vDSqQoGZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一名男子为宝仕奥莎（Preciosa）的一个水晶装置拍摄照片。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103019txDoreph9kgwqMKX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在“Mindcraft 16”展览上，一位参观者正在查看丹麦设计师们展示的作品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103020WsLQ4kdJhx3qKwj9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">意大利设计师 Eleonora Barbareschi（左）和 Alessandra Mantovani 站在他们设计的挂灯下，内部以超现实主义的手法复制了圣彼得大教堂（Saint Peter Basilica）的穹顶。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103020HN1iwKVet4zSZmqx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">参观者查看着一件名为“The Neon Traffic Dealer - TROLLEYS”的装置。</p>\n<h2>聚焦上海时装周</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、品牌秀场</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210302192pWc1C5QvHxiGLb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103021n1jZu4XPabikdh0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103022oAFLYaMDkuwH5B9O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">郭长耀/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103022km4zM6wRbLDFvc8r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">模特在秀场展示各品牌作品。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、时尚街拍</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210302335Id2cROBvjpxSJN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030233A1NtyDsS2CPxbGR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103024PJavuIC3FzO5o4eq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103024rIxhsdYMJ3uZoOaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103025yLNX8SvqsH2OpZk7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">时装周进入第五天，上海街头的“潮人”们。</p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、梵高的耳朵</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103025BMFQbegUwmqTri4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">TIMOTHY A. CLARY/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">由双人艺术家组合 Elmgreen &amp; Dragset 制作的一个 30 英尺（约合 9 米）高的艺术品出现在美国纽约的洛克菲勒中心（Rockefeller Center）外。这个泳池造型的雕塑名为“梵高的耳朵”，将展出至 6 月 3 日。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、额尔齐斯河畔</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103026u0tXJ24L1rnKxGjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">rna/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">俄罗斯鄂木斯克（Omsk），人们在额尔齐斯河畔驻足。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、恒河中的祈祷者</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103026x1pd05hbzYuCHSaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">印度安拉阿巴德（Allahabad），两个男孩在恒河上划着小船经过一个正在祈祷的男子。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、不丹僧侣</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021030276LWqBxUz59DQGaME.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">不丹廷布（Thimphu），几位年轻的僧侣在山坡上休息。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、新加坡“绿肺”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103027NqadysRHJeivS1VK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">新加坡民众在自然保护区的小径上锻炼。<br></p>\n\n"}